overview: (Season 9 Premiere) Who else will join the ranks of the BDK? Resident femme fatales Daizee Haze and Sara Del Rey meet The Osirian Portal in tag team action! The Young Lions Cup is up for grabs when Tim Donst challenges Player Dos. The main event sees Campeones Fire Ant and Soldier Ant defend against perennial rivals, F.I.S.T.
title: CHIKARA A Touch of Class
